### Welcome to The Legend of the BioFire: Utre's Journey
This is a terraria mod that's going to be mixed in with starbound kinda like a cross over, some music wIll be new and mine, new items,new enemies, new Bosses, temples... You know what? multiple cross overs! lol jk copyright I'm going to have to ask the devs of starbound and terraria if I can do this. Planning to release the demo in 2017 full mod release is not planned yet. I may not even release the demo because this doesn't have very many stars on GitHub so if it gets to 58 stars then I will release the demo... once its finished of course.
